---
import { whatsappUrl } from '../../data/landing';
---

<section class="relative px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" id="contacto">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
		<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-cyan-300/20 bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(8,15,31,0.96),rgba(5,8,22,0.96))] p-8 shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(14,165,233,0.15)] sm:p-12 lg:p-16">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(34,211,238,0.18),transparent_28%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,rgba(16,185,129,0.09),transparent_24%)]"></div>
			<div class="relative grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_0.6fr] lg:items-center">
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan-200/75">CTA</p>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Tu negocio ya tiene clientes, ahora necesita una presencia digital profesional.</h2>
					<p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-300">Si quieres una web que se vea premium, explique mejor tu valor y convierta mensajes en oportunidades, este es el siguiente paso.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="flex lg:justify-end">
					<a href={whatsappUrl} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 px-7 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-slate-950 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(34,211,238,0.28)] transition hover:scale-[1.02] hover:bg-cyan-300">
						<i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-xl"></i>
						Cotizar por WhatsApp
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>